Key Match Events: Alperen Şengün scored 23 points, grabbed six rebounds, dished out four assists, and recorded five steals in 37 minutes.
Jalen Green tallied 22 points, Dillon Brooks added 19, and rookie Cam Whitmore chipped in 18.
Post-Match Reflections: Turkish sensation Alperen Şengün delivered a masterclass performance, spearheading Houston's 22nd win of the season.
Houston's victory ensured a commanding win over Dallas, now with a 14-14 record.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game took place at Toyota Center, Houston, Texas, U.S. on January 1, 2025.
